		Croutier was elected to his first term on the Court in 2007. He is a 
		senior partner in a law firm and a member of numerous professional 
		associations.&nbsp; He served as the chairman of both the Rockville Centre We 
		Care September 11th Committee and the Rockville Centre September 11th&nbsp; 
