		<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial" size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font>
		<font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial,sans-serif">Judge 
		McDonough was elected to his first term on the Court in 2009. He is a 
		partner in a Garden City law firm. He was a Deputy Village Attorney for 
		nine years, served on the Village Planning Board and is president of the 
		Friends of Senior Services which aids the Sandel Senior Center. He is a 
		volunteer counsel to the RVC St. Patrick&#8217;s Parade and has coached in 
		local sports leagues.</span><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</td>
